---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Daña Tovar | Smithville City Council">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h1>About Daña</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A third-generation Smithvillian who cares about what happens next.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-section section">
    <div class="container story-container">
      <div class="story-content">
        <p>
          I am a third-generation Smithvillian, and I’ve been in Smithville for over 40 years. The kind of place where people wave from their porches. Where you run into friends at the grocery store and end up talking for 30 minutes. Where Friday nights still mean something.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm not a career politician. I'm a neighbor who has been paying attention. And I think our city council should work the way Smithville works: openly, honestly, and with respect for every person who lives here. 
        </p>
        <p>
          Over the years, I've watched this town grow. We've welcomed new neighbors, seen new businesses open on Main Street, and navigated the challenges that come with change. But through it all, what makes Smithville special hasn't changed. It's the people.
        </p>
        <p>
          My community involvement has never been about building a resume. Whether it's volunteering at local events, supporting our schools, or simply helping out a neighbor in need, I've always believed that if you want a strong community, you have to help build it. I've invested my life here.
        </p>
        
        <blockquote class="pull-quote">
          "I believe our city council should be as approachable as a neighbor over the fence. You shouldn't have to navigate red tape to get a straight answer."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="gallery-section section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">Daña in the Community</h2>
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <!-- Placeholders -->
        <div class="gallery-placeholder">
          <span>[ Community Event Photo ]</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder">
          <span>[ Main Street Photo ]</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder">
          <span>[ Local Park Photo ]</span>
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder">
          <span>[ With Neighbors Photo ]</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="call-to-action-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Join Our Campaign</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Help us keep Smithville strong.</p>
      <a href="/get-involved#volunteer" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 6rem 0;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .text-center {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .story-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .story-content p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .pull-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-highlight);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  
  .gallery-section {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
  }
  
  .gallery-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .gallery-placeholder {
    background-color: #E2E8F0;
    border: 2px dashed #CBD5E1;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #64748B;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  .call-to-action-section {
    padding: 5rem 0;
    background-color: white;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(27, 58, 92, 0.1);
  }
  
  .btn-large {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .gallery-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .pull-quote {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
